{"tid":1942899,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"醜婦的眼淚 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-03-25T10:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T11:27:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6470962a66619cd9b15acc5841f79538dbbcaf","tid":1942899,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T10:40:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200325/20886668/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200325%2F20886668%2F&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn1iy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=75d1c741\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200325%2F20886668%2F&h=1bf5b3a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200325/20886668/</a><br />\n<br />\n醜婦的眼淚 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200325/large/1585045587_c468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200325%2Flarge%2F1585045587_c468.jpg&h=1fe9c6d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《大話西遊之愛你一萬年》截圖<br />\n<br />\n一般情況下，看到別人哭，會令我不知所措，繼而生厭。我很討厭動輒就哭的人。成年人，尤其在香港長大、聽慣《獅子山下》的成年人，有事打落牙齒和血吞，不輕易向人示弱，更不隨便在公眾場合哭。<br />\n<br />\n話雖如此，港女還是會哭的，在她在乎，以及在乎她的男人面前哭。這個可以是一種手段。年輕貌美的女子在她自己的男人面前梨花帶淚、楚楚可憐，男人能不心軟？馬上把她攬在懷中。之前發生過甚麼，一早拋到九霄雲外。<br />\n<br />\n也有與手段無關的哭。傷心到一定程度，但未至於絕望時，女人也會忍不住哭。會自省的男人，這個時候看到女人的眼淚，心中一凜，細想自己做錯了甚麼。到女人對男人完全絕望時，是無淚也無恨的。因為再也沒有感覺。<br />\n<br />\n世人多數以貌取人，一個貌寢老婦若在人前哭泣，絕對不可能獲得同情分；一個貌寢老婦若因為自己做錯事而在人前哭泣，則非但不能獲得同情分，更惹起公憤；一個貌寢老婦若因為自己做錯事，傷害了公眾，而在公眾面前哭泣，叫一眾受害的公眾給甚麼反應好？<br />\n<br />\n慳返你的眼淚吧！香港人不相信鱷魚的眼淚。鱷魚在進食時對着獵物或食物落淚，是一種疾病。有病的話請去見醫生。找身心健康的人來為公眾服務，才是負責任的做法。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"0e699d726fde99673f271667bcfdd369110377a9","tid":1942899,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T10:42:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8083501137c927e1733f1fcbf0959a308befa21","tid":1942899,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf46b46827edec57e6922ac06d1f923fc8d44d7","tid":1942899,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jcfp6YO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJcfp6YO.jpg&h=07e5612a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/titSwqt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtitSwqt.jpg&h=325c8f83&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}